# 2. BUSINESS CONTEXT

We are building a Fiber ISP Operating System for a Philippine FTTH business with the following characteristics:

- The operator manages multiple barangay service areas.
- Each barangay may have a different JV partner.
- Each JV partner may have its own:
  - capital contribution
  - revenue share
  - opex allocation rule
  - capex recovery rule
  - reporting requirements
- Each barangay has:
  - households / subscribers
  - network assets
  - installation workflows
  - service tickets
  - billing accounts
  - collection status
  - technician assignments
  - profitability metrics

The system must support:
- operational segmentation by barangay
- partner segmentation by JV entity
- strict data partitioning
- consolidated corporate-level reporting

