# 4. NON-NEGOTIABLE PLATFORM PRINCIPLES

## 4.1 Multi-Tenancy / Segmentation
The platform must support logical segmentation at minimum by:
- company / operator
- barangay
- joint venture partner
- users and roles
- subscribers
