## 4.2 Auditability
Every important mutation must be auditable:
- who created
- who updated
- when
- previous value
- new value
- source module
- reason code where applicable

## 4.3 Financial Traceability
Any amount affecting:
- invoice
- payment
- adjustment
- penalty
- write-off
- partner share
- settlement
must be reconstructible from ledger-grade records.

## 4.4 Telecom Operational Traceability
A subscriber must be traceable to:
- barangay
- service address
- plan
- ONT / CPE
- drop fiber
- distribution point / box
- splitter
- PON port
- OLT
- assigned technician history
- billing history
- ticket history

## 4.5 Safe Delivery
Do not build the whole platform blindly.
Deliver in phases with acceptance gates.

